    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="structfaiss_1_1pq__code__distance_1_1QueryTables" kindref="compound">QueryTables</ref> manages the various ways of searching an <ref refid="structfaiss_1_1IndexIVFPQ" kindref="compound">IndexIVFPQ</ref>. The code contains a lot of branches, depending on:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>metric_type: are we computing L2 or Inner product similarity?</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>by_residual: do we encode raw vectors or residuals?</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>use_precomputed_table: are x_R|x_C tables precomputed?</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>polysemous_ht: are we filtering with polysemous codes? </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
